1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 4]

2
00:00:16,130 --> 00:00:16,809
Put me down!

3
00:00:17,170 --> 00:00:17,929
Don't move!

4
00:00:23,090 --> 00:00:23,929
What are you up to?

5
00:00:26,650 --> 00:00:27,889
You've caused such a scene.

6
00:00:28,570 --> 00:00:30,569
Aren't you afraid my father will hold you accountable tomorrow?

7
00:00:31,450 --> 00:00:32,889
She's hallucinating from opium use.

8
00:00:33,570 --> 00:00:34,929
She won't remember anything!

9
00:00:34,930 --> 00:00:35,929
As long as you keep quiet,

10
00:00:36,210 --> 00:00:37,169
no one will find out.

11
00:00:41,410 --> 00:00:42,929
I admit I underestimated you.

12
00:00:44,930 --> 00:00:45,609
Oh?

13
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:49,209
You're the mastermind

14
00:00:50,210 --> 00:00:51,409
behind the bat incident.

15
00:00:51,890 --> 00:00:52,569
Right?

16
00:00:52,890 --> 00:00:53,889
Before the wedding,

17
00:00:54,010 --> 00:00:56,209
a woman claiming to be our maid visited

18
00:00:56,810 --> 00:00:58,489
the lantern shop to inspect lanterns.

19
00:00:58,930 --> 00:01:01,009
But no maid from our household ever went.

20
00:01:01,210 --> 00:01:02,329
On the wedding day,

21
00:01:02,450 --> 00:01:04,729
you applied bat grass scent on my father

22
00:01:05,130 --> 00:01:06,529
only to "heroically" save him afterward,

23
00:01:07,410 --> 00:01:09,529
so that he would see you in a new light.

24
00:01:13,130 --> 00:01:14,409
Why did you use Nanxi

25
00:01:14,410 --> 00:01:16,209
to tell me about the bat grass?

26
00:01:16,770 --> 00:01:17,849
What's your purpose?

27
00:01:18,410 --> 00:01:19,649
I just wanted to see

28
00:01:20,170 --> 00:01:21,529
whether you're truly a wastrel

29
00:01:21,890 --> 00:01:23,129
or just pretending.

30
00:01:24,890 --> 00:01:26,329
I don't understand what you're saying.

31
00:01:29,650 --> 00:01:31,129
On the wedding night,

32
00:01:32,530 --> 00:01:35,209
you secretly sent a letter to Second concubine,

33
00:01:35,410 --> 00:01:36,929
luring her to the pond.

34
00:01:37,450 --> 00:01:39,009
You hired someone to scare her as a ghost,

35
00:01:39,010 --> 00:01:40,569
trying to drown her.

36
00:01:43,210 --> 00:01:44,649
But that's my mother!

37
00:01:44,890 --> 00:01:46,169
My closest kin.

38
00:01:46,450 --> 00:01:47,609
Why would I harm her?

39
00:01:50,530 --> 00:01:51,329
The Eldest Young Master is

40
00:01:51,490 --> 00:01:53,769
the biological son of the deceased Madam.

41
00:01:54,610 --> 00:01:56,249
When the Madam was pregnant,

42
00:01:56,250 --> 00:01:57,249
her husband died.

43
00:01:57,770 --> 00:01:58,809
But her family

44
00:01:58,930 --> 00:02:00,769
was Wu county's wealthiest.

45
00:02:01,090 --> 00:02:02,209
So they made Master

46
00:02:02,290 --> 00:02:03,849
marry into the family as her husband.

47
00:02:03,850 --> 00:02:05,609
Eldest Young Master could have a father.

48
00:02:06,010 --> 00:02:07,569
Master was handsome,

49
00:02:07,890 --> 00:02:09,849
So he caught the eye of

50
00:02:09,850 --> 00:02:10,649
the Madam's sister.

51
00:02:11,570 --> 00:02:12,929
After his father-in-law passed away,

52
00:02:13,330 --> 00:02:15,409
Master married her as Second concubine.

53
00:02:16,370 --> 00:02:17,769
After the Madame died,

54
00:02:18,090 --> 00:02:18,769
the Eldest Young Master

55
00:02:18,850 --> 00:02:19,569
was adopted by

56
00:02:19,570 --> 00:02:21,089
the infertile Second concubine.

57
00:02:21,490 --> 00:02:22,569
All these years,

58
00:02:23,010 --> 00:02:24,969
you've pretended to be a wastrel to survive.

59
00:02:25,890 --> 00:02:26,449
Your purpose

60
00:02:27,450 --> 00:02:28,089
is revenge against

61
00:02:28,090 --> 00:02:29,569
your birth mother's murderer.

62
00:02:30,330 --> 00:02:31,689
The murderer is Second concubine.

63
00:02:33,850 --> 00:02:35,009
You know so much.

64
00:02:35,890 --> 00:02:37,369
Aren't you afraid I'll kill you?

65
00:02:38,970 --> 00:02:41,329
I've killed myself countless times

66
00:02:41,730 --> 00:02:42,849
to stand here today.

67
00:02:44,410 --> 00:02:45,689
You think I fear you?

68
00:02:49,530 --> 00:02:50,529
You came to Zhou Manor

69
00:02:50,890 --> 00:02:52,649
to take revenge on my mother?

70
00:02:54,010 --> 00:02:54,809
Eldest Young Master,

71
00:02:55,410 --> 00:02:56,729
everyone carries secrets.

72
00:02:57,010 --> 00:02:58,569
Worry about yourself.

73
00:03:03,570 --> 00:03:05,089
Since our goals align,

74
00:03:05,410 --> 00:03:06,729
I can be useful to you.

75
00:03:07,410 --> 00:03:08,689
I don't understand you.

76
00:03:09,250 --> 00:03:10,089
Tell me.

77
00:03:10,730 --> 00:03:11,769
I can help you.

78
00:03:14,490 --> 00:03:15,169
Help me?

79
00:03:17,610 --> 00:03:18,329
You're not worthy.

80
00:03:33,930 --> 00:03:34,809
Master.

81
00:03:35,090 --> 00:03:36,849
Do you think this golden dress

82
00:03:38,450 --> 00:03:39,289
I'm wearing is beautiful?

83
00:03:40,290 --> 00:03:41,329
You once said

84
00:03:42,890 --> 00:03:45,209
you'd love only me in this lifetime.

85
00:03:45,570 --> 00:03:47,649
Why did you take others then?

86
00:03:47,730 --> 00:03:49,889
Such devotion, sister.

87
00:03:50,330 --> 00:03:51,289
You've pinned your entire life

88
00:03:51,290 --> 00:03:53,329
on one man.

89
00:03:53,610 --> 00:03:55,089
None of it was real, was it?

90
00:03:55,930 --> 00:03:56,769
Little did you know,

91
00:03:57,330 --> 00:03:58,529
you're the...

92
00:03:58,530 --> 00:03:59,169
Do you love her?

93
00:03:59,650 --> 00:04:02,649
pitiful creature.

94
00:04:02,650 --> 00:04:03,529
No!

95
00:04:04,370 --> 00:04:05,369
You love me.

96
00:04:06,690 --> 00:04:07,889
You love me!

97
00:04:16,850 --> 00:04:17,609
Did you see?

98
00:04:18,010 --> 00:04:19,849
Second concubine was burned beyond recognition.

99
00:04:20,250 --> 00:04:20,969
I saw.

100
00:04:20,970 --> 00:04:21,849
Too horrifying.

101
00:04:22,010 --> 00:04:22,569
Stop looking.

102
00:04:23,170 --> 00:04:24,089
Dismissed.
- Yes.

103
00:04:24,210 --> 00:04:25,209
Yes, Second Young Master.

104
00:04:27,410 --> 00:04:27,969
Concubine.

105
00:04:30,370 --> 00:04:32,409
Just yesterday I met her.

106
00:04:33,890 --> 00:04:34,969
Today she's gone.

107
00:04:35,890 --> 00:04:37,169
The police have sent investigators.

108
00:04:37,770 --> 00:04:38,609
I'll handle things here.

109
00:04:39,130 --> 00:04:40,369
You should return and rest.

110
00:04:40,890 --> 00:04:41,849
Thank you, Second Young Master.

111
00:04:42,570 --> 00:04:43,489
I shall take my leave then.

112
00:04:44,770 --> 00:04:45,569
Wait.

113
00:04:50,730 --> 00:04:51,529
Surely

114
00:04:51,163 --> 00:04:54,234
[Jin Shi'an, the Patrol Captain]

115
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:54,289
this is the newly arrived Fifth concubine?

116
00:05:02,890 --> 00:05:03,729
Captain Yu.

117
00:05:05,290 --> 00:05:06,569
The smoke is thick and it's crowded here.

118
00:05:06,770 --> 00:05:09,289
So I asked her to rest first.

119
00:05:11,570 --> 00:05:12,729
If the smoke bothers you,

120
00:05:13,410 --> 00:05:14,449
a damp cloth might help.

121
00:05:15,570 --> 00:05:16,329
Unnecessary.

122
00:05:19,570 --> 00:05:20,569
Nice to meet you.

123
00:05:21,810 --> 00:05:22,689
Captain Yu.

124
00:05:27,170 --> 00:05:32,289
[Police Station]

125
00:05:40,890 --> 00:05:41,289
Xiaoman.

126
00:05:44,170 --> 00:05:45,089
Shi'an.

127
00:05:46,170 --> 00:05:47,849
My sister couldn't have killed herself.

128
00:05:48,610 --> 00:05:50,329
She must have been murdered!

129
00:05:51,850 --> 00:05:53,249
Can you investigate further?

130
00:05:53,730 --> 00:05:54,649
I beg you,

131
00:05:55,090 --> 00:05:56,649
please help me investigate again.

132
00:05:59,170 --> 00:06:00,409
Take the compensation from the Zhou family

133
00:06:01,290 --> 00:06:02,289
and move on with your life.

134
00:06:03,570 --> 00:06:05,169
If Chuxue were still alive,

135
00:06:06,170 --> 00:06:07,809
she wouldn't want you like this.

136
00:06:09,290 --> 00:06:09,969
But

137
00:06:10,890 --> 00:06:11,969
my sister...

138
00:06:13,330 --> 00:06:15,689
If she wasn't murdered,

139
00:06:17,610 --> 00:06:20,449
then why the rush to cremate her body?

140
00:06:21,610 --> 00:06:23,569
This is clearly destroying evidence!

141
00:06:23,570 --> 00:06:24,689
Shi'an!

142
00:06:25,330 --> 00:06:26,889
I will not rest until I uncover the truth

143
00:06:27,410 --> 00:06:28,809
behind Chuxue's death

144
00:06:30,170 --> 00:06:31,169
and give you the answers!

145
00:06:31,330 --> 00:06:31,889
Alright?

146
00:06:33,330 --> 00:06:34,449
Shi'an,

147
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:38,569
can I trust you?

148
00:06:39,730 --> 00:06:40,529
Silly girl.

149
00:06:41,570 --> 00:06:42,809
You may doubt others,

150
00:06:44,170 --> 00:06:45,409
but you must trust me.

151
00:06:50,730 --> 00:06:52,169
The Zhou family paid a hefty compensation,

152
00:06:53,410 --> 00:06:54,689
her sister took the money.

153
00:06:56,490 --> 00:06:57,169
I think

154
00:06:57,730 --> 00:06:59,129
she won't pursue Chuxue's death anymore.

155
00:07:01,090 --> 00:07:02,569
Then I'll trouble Captain Yu

156
00:07:02,690 --> 00:07:04,089
to handle the case files

157
00:07:04,090 --> 00:07:04,969
and the autopsy report promptly.

158
00:07:05,850 --> 00:07:07,369
After the case concludes,

159
00:07:08,770 --> 00:07:10,449
your acting patrol captain position

160
00:07:10,810 --> 00:07:11,689
will become official.

161
00:07:12,370 --> 00:07:14,569
After all, Director Zhou and Master are cousins.

162
00:07:14,810 --> 00:07:16,249
are cousins.

163
00:07:18,370 --> 00:07:19,209
Rest assured.

164
00:07:20,450 --> 00:07:21,969
I've assigned trusted subordinates to

165
00:07:23,570 --> 00:07:26,329
destroy evidence in the backyard shed.

166
00:07:38,410 --> 00:07:39,649
Xiaoman, why are you here?

167
00:07:40,010 --> 00:07:40,569
Move!

168
00:07:40,730 --> 00:07:41,449
Xiaoman, don't be impulsive!

169
00:07:41,570 --> 00:07:42,849
Why is that gun pointed at me?

170
00:07:43,690 --> 00:07:44,809
Move!

171
00:07:52,490 --> 00:07:53,089
Ye Xiaoman!

172
00:07:53,730 --> 00:07:54,729
Leave the autopsy report!

173
00:07:54,730 --> 00:07:55,689
Put the gun down!

174
00:07:56,690 --> 00:07:57,249
Go back!

175
00:08:00,010 --> 00:08:01,289
Why did you lie to me?

176
00:08:02,490 --> 00:08:03,289
Give it to me!

177
00:08:03,570 --> 00:08:04,849
I'm protecting you!

178
00:08:07,330 --> 00:08:08,209
Liar!

179
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:30,329
Nice to meet you.

180
00:08:31,170 --> 00:08:32,529
How should I address you?

181
00:08:32,930 --> 00:08:34,289
Call her Fifth Concubine.

182
00:08:35,450 --> 00:08:36,289
Does her name

183
00:08:37,330 --> 00:08:37,929
matter?

184
00:08:37,930 --> 00:08:38,729
Yes.

185
00:08:39,210 --> 00:08:40,489
Please cooperate, Fifth Concubine.

186
00:08:48,490 --> 00:08:49,329
My name is Ye

187
00:08:52,490 --> 00:08:53,289
Zhiqiu

188
00:08:58,730 --> 00:08:59,569
What a coincidence.

189
00:09:01,250 --> 00:09:02,769
I had a friend before

190
00:09:03,970 --> 00:09:04,729
also surnamed Ye.

191
00:09:05,410 --> 00:09:06,129
But now

192
00:09:06,130 --> 00:09:07,569
we're no longer in contact.

193
00:09:10,330 --> 00:09:11,089
I'm tired.

194
00:09:11,570 --> 00:09:12,449
May I return first?

195
00:09:12,450 --> 00:09:13,169
No.

196
00:09:14,570 --> 00:09:15,529
The Second Concubine lost her life

197
00:09:15,810 --> 00:09:16,729
in a fire last night.

198
00:09:17,490 --> 00:09:18,329
Everyone in Zhou Manor

199
00:09:18,530 --> 00:09:19,369
must be investigated.

200
00:09:20,850 --> 00:09:22,569
Captain Yu makes a valid point.

201
00:09:25,730 --> 00:09:27,649
Fifth Concubine was with my father last night.

202
00:09:28,530 --> 00:09:29,729
Why don't you investigate him first?

203
00:09:31,970 --> 00:09:33,809
Your superior, Director Zhou,

204
00:09:34,010 --> 00:09:35,369
and my father are cousins.

205
00:09:35,450 --> 00:09:36,569
Not just the police station,

206
00:09:37,090 --> 00:09:39,089
all of Wu County belongs to Zhou family.

207
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:42,849
Eldest Young Master Zhou,

208
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:45,249
you have a sharp tongue.

209
00:09:46,010 --> 00:09:46,969
At least our words

210
00:09:47,290 --> 00:09:49,649
aren't real guns!

211
00:09:50,730 --> 00:09:51,609
Captain Yu.

212
00:09:52,290 --> 00:09:53,569
My brother speaks truth.

213
00:09:56,170 --> 00:09:57,729
My mother burned to death inside.

214
00:09:58,330 --> 00:09:59,729
Instead of doing your duty,

215
00:09:59,730 --> 00:10:01,009
you're here chatting up

216
00:10:01,010 --> 00:10:02,169
a young and pretty concubine.

217
00:10:02,330 --> 00:10:03,129
What right do you have

218
00:10:03,130 --> 00:10:04,449
to demand civil conversation?

219
00:10:07,970 --> 00:10:08,769
Fifth Concubine,

220
00:10:09,170 --> 00:10:09,689
let's go.

221
00:10:36,490 --> 00:10:37,289
What do you want?

222
00:10:39,210 --> 00:10:40,569
You know that policeman?

223
00:10:44,730 --> 00:10:45,769
You overthink.

224
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:51,209
Did you set that fire?

225
00:10:53,290 --> 00:10:54,289
Weren't you the one pulling me

226
00:10:54,290 --> 00:10:55,769
out of her room yesterday?

227
00:10:56,290 --> 00:10:57,929
Wouldn't you know if I started the fire?

228
00:10:58,690 --> 00:10:59,569
It's actually you

229
00:10:59,890 --> 00:11:00,969
who's more suspicious, isn't it?

230
00:11:01,170 --> 00:11:02,449
After all, the way she died

231
00:11:02,850 --> 00:11:04,129
is exactly like

232
00:11:04,570 --> 00:11:05,569
your mother back then.

233
00:11:06,450 --> 00:11:07,529
Whether I did it or not,

234
00:11:07,570 --> 00:11:09,489
the investigation will reveal the facts.

235
00:11:10,090 --> 00:11:11,689
I just need to make sure it's not you.

236
00:11:14,010 --> 00:11:14,489
The facts?

237
00:11:15,770 --> 00:11:16,649
The so-called facts

238
00:11:17,010 --> 00:11:18,089
might be that the entire Wu County

239
00:11:18,090 --> 00:11:19,089
belongs to the Zhou family.

240
00:11:19,410 --> 00:11:20,569
The Zhou family dictates

241
00:11:21,170 --> 00:11:22,089
what is black

242
00:11:22,490 --> 00:11:23,249
and what is white.

243
00:11:25,690 --> 00:11:26,809
Whatever you want to do,

244
00:11:27,170 --> 00:11:28,169
I can help you.

245
00:11:28,530 --> 00:11:29,809
I can protect you.

246
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,586
[Zhang Jinbao, driver]

247
00:11:33,610 --> 00:11:34,569
[Zhang Jinbao, driver]
Master has urgent business.

248
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:36,209
All members are summoned to the hall.

249
00:11:38,530 --> 00:11:39,169
Who is he?

250
00:11:39,690 --> 00:11:40,649
Driver Zhang Jinbao.

251
00:11:40,850 --> 00:11:41,449
One of us.

252
00:11:45,170 --> 00:11:46,289
Head to the hall separately.

253
00:11:46,530 --> 00:11:47,169
You go first.

254
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:50,889
Zhou Yimo, I warn you.

255
00:11:52,450 --> 00:11:53,529
Lives are at stake.

256
00:11:54,530 --> 00:11:55,529
Don't play games.

257
00:11:55,890 --> 00:11:56,569
I promise you.

258
00:12:09,970 --> 00:12:12,289
[Matriarch of the He family]

259
00:12:12,330 --> 00:12:14,329
Back then, our He family was prestigious

260
00:12:14,490 --> 00:12:15,729
and respectable in Wu County.

261
00:12:16,890 --> 00:12:17,929
Zhou Huaiqian

262
00:12:18,010 --> 00:12:20,329
you received favors from He-family master

263
00:12:20,850 --> 00:12:21,289
and thus

264
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:23,209
were able to marry his two most

265
00:12:23,210 --> 00:12:24,249
beloved daughters.

266
00:12:25,490 --> 00:12:26,729
Now Wangshu

267
00:12:27,650 --> 00:12:29,249
has also met a tragic end.

268
00:12:30,410 --> 00:12:31,889
Although she was born out of wedlock,

269
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:33,969
I watched her grow up.

270
00:12:34,890 --> 00:12:36,809
If you don't give me an explanation,

271
00:12:36,970 --> 00:12:38,889
where will our He family's reputation be?

272
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:41,809
Mother, rest assured.

273
00:12:42,250 --> 00:12:42,929
This matter

274
00:12:43,650 --> 00:12:44,849
will be thoroughly investigated.

275
00:12:46,130 --> 00:12:46,529
Master,

276
00:12:46,930 --> 00:12:47,569
fifth Concubine has arrived.

277
00:12:54,170 --> 00:12:54,809
Master,

278
00:12:55,610 --> 00:12:56,969
so she is the fifth Concubine?

279
00:12:57,930 --> 00:12:58,649
It seems Second Concubine's

280
00:12:58,810 --> 00:13:01,089
family is here to seek justice.

281
00:13:03,490 --> 00:13:04,169
Last night,

282
00:13:04,770 --> 00:13:05,689
where were you?

283
00:13:06,770 --> 00:13:07,529
Last night,

284
00:13:08,210 --> 00:13:10,009
I stayed in my own room.

285
00:13:10,530 --> 00:13:11,529
I went nowhere at all.

286
00:13:11,570 --> 00:13:12,169
Master

287
00:13:12,570 --> 00:13:13,449
she's lying.

288
00:13:15,090 --> 00:13:15,729
Yesterday,

289
00:13:16,250 --> 00:13:17,249
when I went to the kitchen

290
00:13:17,250 --> 00:13:18,889
to fetch bird's nest for Second Concubine,

291
00:13:19,370 --> 00:13:20,209
I saw

292
00:13:20,490 --> 00:13:21,209
her being dragged

293
00:13:21,210 --> 00:13:23,169
out of the room by the Eldest Young Master.

294
00:13:26,450 --> 00:13:27,369
I heard

295
00:13:28,090 --> 00:13:29,249
the second concubine shouting inside,

296
00:13:29,610 --> 00:13:30,329
"Don't burn it!

297
00:13:30,450 --> 00:13:31,249
Don't burn it!"

298
00:13:32,490 --> 00:13:33,609
You bitch!

299
00:13:33,970 --> 00:13:35,329
So it was you!

300
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:37,969
As long as Zhou Yimo and I deny it,

301
00:13:38,370 --> 00:13:39,529
her witness is meaningless.

302
00:13:39,610 --> 00:13:40,729
Sorry I'm late.

303
00:13:41,250 --> 00:13:41,809
He's here.

304
00:13:43,890 --> 00:13:44,449
Grandmother.

305
00:13:44,490 --> 00:13:45,209
My dear grandson,

306
00:13:45,330 --> 00:13:45,889
get up.

307
00:13:46,010 --> 00:13:46,569
Yimo,

308
00:13:47,250 --> 00:13:47,809
let me ask you!

309
00:13:48,730 --> 00:13:50,329
Did you see Second Concubine

310
00:13:50,970 --> 00:13:52,249
and Fifth Concubine last night?

311
00:13:53,090 --> 00:13:53,569
Yes.

312
00:13:54,010 --> 00:13:54,769
Of course.

313
00:13:56,490 --> 00:13:57,489
I can help you.

314
00:13:57,730 --> 00:13:59,369
I can protect you.

315
00:14:01,970 --> 00:14:02,929
It's over.

316
00:14:03,490 --> 00:14:05,609
I knew that bitch was lying.

317
00:14:06,890 --> 00:14:08,169
How dare you lie to me!

318
00:14:09,650 --> 00:14:10,329
Father.

319
00:14:11,370 --> 00:14:12,529
What's he up to now?

320
00:14:14,610 --> 00:14:16,209
Not only did I see Fifth Concubine,

321
00:14:16,850 --> 00:14:18,449
but I also discovered something important.

322
00:14:19,370 --> 00:14:21,529
Zhou Yimo, you betrayed me!

323
00:14:27,490 --> 00:14:29,009
Why did you kidnap my private doctor?

324
00:14:29,530 --> 00:14:30,529
Care to guess, father?

325
00:14:30,770 --> 00:14:32,289
What medications has he been prescribing

326
00:14:32,570 --> 00:14:33,649
to Second Concubine all these years?

327
00:14:36,890 --> 00:14:38,369
Clozapine,

328
00:14:38,970 --> 00:14:39,849
Reserpine,

329
00:14:40,730 --> 00:14:41,649
Bupropion.

330
00:14:41,650 --> 00:14:43,249
Zhou Yimo, what are you doing?

331
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:44,369
Trazodone.

332
00:14:44,370 --> 00:14:45,129
Just wait for the show.

333
00:14:45,130 --> 00:14:46,369
Estradiol.

334
00:14:46,650 --> 00:14:47,569
What are these?

335
00:14:47,970 --> 00:14:48,649
I can't understand them.

336
00:14:48,970 --> 00:14:49,569
Father,

337
00:14:50,650 --> 00:14:51,449
these

338
00:14:53,130 --> 00:14:53,889
are all Western medications

339
00:14:53,890 --> 00:14:55,729
that render you impotent.

340
00:14:55,730 --> 00:14:56,369
What?

341
00:14:56,770 --> 00:14:57,449
Calm down.

342
00:14:59,210 --> 00:15:00,609
Fifth Concubine refused to admit it

343
00:15:02,010 --> 00:15:03,689
to protect your dignity.

344
00:15:05,810 --> 00:15:07,529
Yesterday I learned Second Concubine

345
00:15:07,530 --> 00:15:08,369
was feeling down,

346
00:15:08,370 --> 00:15:09,489
so I went to talk with her.

347
00:15:09,690 --> 00:15:10,409
Just arrived

348
00:15:10,410 --> 00:15:11,769
and found Fifth Concubine there

349
00:15:11,930 --> 00:15:13,769
confronting her with prescription records.

350
00:15:13,850 --> 00:15:14,849
At first I thought

351
00:15:14,850 --> 00:15:16,169
Fifth Concubine was causing trouble,

352
00:15:16,370 --> 00:15:18,169
so I dragged her out of the room.

353
00:15:18,490 --> 00:15:19,409
This morning

354
00:15:19,570 --> 00:15:20,929
I went to the hospital and discovered

355
00:15:21,490 --> 00:15:22,369
it was actually

356
00:15:22,370 --> 00:15:24,169
Second Concubine drugging you all along.

357
00:15:25,810 --> 00:15:27,889
I would never betray you!

358
00:15:29,570 --> 00:15:30,569
Why would you do this to me?

359
00:15:30,570 --> 00:15:31,569
Why?

360
00:15:32,090 --> 00:15:33,329
Calm down, father.

361
00:15:33,650 --> 00:15:34,849
If she can't have you, she'll ruin you.

362
00:15:35,810 --> 00:15:36,809
You've known the Second Concubine

363
00:15:36,810 --> 00:15:37,969
for a long time.

364
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:40,529
So that's what this is about.
